{"tid":2301370,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"篠崎 泫 勁似我中四個中文老師","createTime":"2020-11-26T09:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T09:23:58.000Z","uid":379666,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8fdb9e1615da361ea05e16050e05858563ff9b","tid":2301370,"uid":379666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:03:29.000Z","msg":"個老師當時畢業冇耐 對教育好有熱誠 同學生相處得好好 幾乎打成一片<br />\n佢隻眼又係好大 依家諗返連把聲都勁似<br />\n佢仲要勁pure 我地班仔私底下叫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最記得有次佢著咗條勁緊勁貼身既皮褲<br />\n果陣我地做緊工作紙<br />\n我坐最後一排 佢行到我右手邊 然後我左手邊條友問佢問題 佢就貼住我彎腰同個同學講野（示意圖後補）<br />\n佢對肉大腿同對波全程貼住我背脊 我幾乎感受到佢既體溫 我當時完全唔敢郁 我好驚只要一郁佢就會發現依家我地個姿勢有幾尷尬 然後即刻彈開<br />\n但佢又好似完全唔介意<br />\n<br />\n依家諗返都扯扯地"},{"pid":"8a3bbf30ccd1496460fbdbc08e4796cf42a53eee","tid":2301370,"uid":384451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bb87359b41b7aea268c6e08e2e4e33f08e13e63","tid":2301370,"uid":379666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a3bbf30ccd1496460fbdbc08e4796cf42a53eee","tid":2301370,"uid":384451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"真人真事"},{"pid":"458bc0d5915bfe329ac55a102596a2c319a71023","tid":2301370,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"有冇圖片"},{"pid":"c273f493dc9edbfb9071a16a0980f85eb69b1827","tid":2301370,"uid":212771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"我入到黎"},{"pid":"3db82da51913c496c3958164a29a2e1bee68d12e","tid":2301370,"uid":158145,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:12:48.000Z","msg":"條女好撚正"},{"pid":"6bdf38ff3023c85272ac863281da29cb725f4bdf","tid":2301370,"uid":379666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"458bc0d5915bfe329ac55a102596a2c319a71023","tid":2301370,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dis